  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Investigation of pupillometry as guide for extubation readiness in anesthetized children.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Can a pupil metric be used to make extubation more safe in anesthetized children?&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
